text: Karanovac () is a Serbo-Croatian toponym, derived from masculine given name Karan. It may refer to: *Karanovac, Petrovo, Bosnia and Herzegovina *Karanovac, Varvarin, Serbia *Old name for Kraljevo, Serbia ==See also== *Karanović, surname *Karanovci, placename Category:Serbo-Croatian place names
title: Karanovac
